description:
The Project Management Executive will gain experience in cross-functional teams of Business Development, Operations, Engineering and Customer Success.
You will be wearing multiple hats while designing creative solutions to our customers’ greatest challenges!

What you will do:

Research
Research, conduct requirement gatherings and report on clients’ needs;
Analyse and report on competitors and industry trends;
Brainstorm and document new features and modules;
Database management:
Data Policing - Develop, maintain data and databases of people and/or companies for them to be used as leads for sales and marketing engagement;
Streamline the data collection process and identify new opportunities for process improvement;
Project Management:
Support our Enterprise Account Lead in drafting business reports and proposals, and the execution of projects;
Assist in managing our third-party vendors;
Provide project co-ordination and administrative support including meeting preparation, scheduling and status reports, documentation;
Optimise process to balance between speed and scalability and continuously improve the efficiency of the current processes;
Propose options for product improvement and product partners;
Ensure projects are completed properly, timely, within budgets, with all requirements fulfilled;
Others:
Test and monitor the products for quality assurance purposes;
Work to anticipate upcoming needs and hurdles; good instinct when to ask for advice. -|-
A degree in Mathematics, Statistics, Engineering or Computer Science preferred;
At least 2 years of experience in similar roles of project management, data analysis and reporting;
Positive attitude;
An analytical mind and a resourceful problem solver, with a strong sense of ownership;
Attention to details, and good time management skills;
Highly organised, able to prioritise and create order in chaos;
Strong verbal and written communication skills;
Excellent presentation and planning skills;
Eagerness to learn new skills, gain new knowledge and stay updated with technological and market trends.

